      <title>大型银行称特朗普尽管言辞激烈但仍然看好美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/deutsche-barclays-say-trump-is-dollar-bullish-despite-rhetoric</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街策略师表示，尽管共和党人唐纳德·特朗普最近表示他更希望美元贬值，但如果特朗普再次出任总统，美元将升值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/deutsche-barclays-say-trump-is-dollar-bullish-despite-rhetoric</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 11:28:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
